=== Pilot phase plan ===
>> pilot_step_02: validate chat templates + token scoring + explicit trait controls
>> pilot_step_03: train/load target donor + neutral-control donor; confirm transfer
>> pilot_step_04: extract explicit + donor representations
>> pilot_step_05: find rank 1-4 causal subspace (patch-in + ablation)
>> pilot_step_06: score candidate rows; compare high/low/random deciles
>> pilot_step_07: selection-only beam search to K=16
>> pilot_step_08: clean replay on eval_dev only
>> pilot_step_09: alpha-star phase diagram if behavior null but state strong
>> pilot_step_10: correct-CoT selection, then checksum carriers if needed
>> pilot_step_11: freeze best context; open eval_final once
>> pilot_step_12: causal mediation, null searches, final report
